### Use `useOffset` Hook in Recharts (JSX)

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/API/hooks/useOffset.mdx

This snippet demonstrates how to import and use the `useOffset` hook from Recharts within a functional React component. The hook calculates and returns the pixel offset of the chart's plot area from its edges, which is useful for layout and positioning logic. This hook can be used in any Recharts chart component like `<AreaChart/>` or `<LineChart/>`.

```jsx
